casebody.data:
Wynkoop et al., Respondents, v. Osborne et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. June 22, 1889.)

Argued before Barker," P. J., and Dwight and Macomber, JJ.

No opinion. Court declines to consider the appeal, for the reasons stated in opinion of Dwight, J., in Palmyra v. Wynkoop, 6 N. Y. Supp. 62, (decided at the present term.)»
